  "description": "A turbulent, fast-moving stream or river rushes over and around large, dark rocks and boulders. The water is foamy and white where it crashes and swirls, creating a dynamic and energetic scene. The surrounding landscape features trees and vegetation, some with green foliage and others appearing bare. A fallen tree trunk lies across the water in one section, adding to the rugged and natural feel. The light is diffused, suggesting overcast conditions or a dense forest canopy. The overall impression is one of raw power and natural beauty.",
